### 
### 
###

###
### This mod changes the Diamond Chest to use Money instead of Diamond Keys. Feel free to download and change the BaseValueConstant
### on the last line from 5000000.0 to whatever you want it to cost. (5000000 mil seemed like a nice end game value)
###

SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,Sanctuary3_P),/Game/PatchDLC/DiamondLootChest/InteractiveObjects/DiamondChest/Data/UIData_DiamondKeyUsePrompt.UIData_DiamondKeyUsePrompt,ActionText,0,,Use Money ([cashicon]%i)
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,Sanctuary3_P),/Game/PatchDLC/DiamondLootChest/InteractiveObjects/DiamondChest/Data/UIData_DiamondKeyUsePrompt.UIData_DiamondKeyUsePrompt,CurrencyType,0,,/Game/Gear/_Shared/_Design/InventoryCategories/InventoryCategory_Money
SparkLevelPatchEntry,(1,1,0,Sanctuary3_P),/Game/PatchDLC/DiamondLootChest/InteractiveObjects/DiamondChest/Data/UIData_DiamondKeyUsePrompt.UIData_DiamondKeyUsePrompt,Cost.BaseValueConstant,0,,50000000.0
